title: Cathartic Moments
description:
Pablo Torre, Domonique Foxworth and Monica McNutt debate if Joel Embiid’s buzzer-beater last night against the Raptors was a cathartic moment for the 76ers and what Jay Wright’s retirement means for college basketball.
